This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Gerald Dachs <gda@dachsweb.de>
                             Based on Klaus Schmidingers svdrpdemo plugin

Project's homepage:          https://svn.origo.ethz.ch/yavdr/trunk/vdr-plugin-shutdown/

Latest version available at: https://svn.origo.ethz.ch/yavdr/trunk/vdr-plugin-shutdown/

